<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٢٢ - <span class="c1">"الْأَمْرُ"</span>: الِاقْتِضَا لِفِعْلٍ غَيْرِ <span class="c4">[كَفْ]</span> ... مَا لَمْ يُفَدْ بِنَحْوِ <span class="c1">"كُفَّ"</span> أَمْرُ <span class="c4">[كَفْ]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٥٢٣ - كَـ <span class="c1">"لِتَصُمْ"</span> وَ <span class="c4">[صَلِّ]</span>، وَ <span class="c4">[النَّهْيُ]</span>: طَلَبْ ... كَفٍّ بِغَيْرِ <span class="c4">[نَحْوِ]</span> <span class="c1">"كُفَّ"</span> يُجْتَنَبْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٥٢٤ - كَـ <span class="c1">"لَا تَبِعْ"</span>، وَلَيْسَ الِاسْتِعْلَاءُ ... شَرْطًا، وَلَا <span class="c4">[يُشْتَرَطُ]</span> <span class="c4">[الْعَلَاءُ]</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
